Synopsis:
Siddharth (Kalyan Ram), who lives in Hyderabad, is fascinated by the concept of doppelgangers (lookalikes). He keeps searching for his lookalikes, and much to his surprise, he finds not one but two of them (Manjunath Hegde and Michael). Soon the three meet, and Siddharth takes the help of the other two to make Ishika (Ashika Ranganath) fall for him. When everything is going well, Siddharth and Manjunath get to know the unknown side of Michael aka Bipin Roy, which shocks them. Who is this Michael? What is his backstory? What did Siddharth and Manjunath do after knowing about Michael?

snippet.title: Climate protester run over by lorry in Germany
snippet.description:
A climate protester in Germany was hit by a truck after an enraged driver escalated a blocking protest.

A group of protesters were planted in the road when they set upon by the irate lorry driver.

The driver than started running over one of the protesters before stopping.

#climate #germany #protest

Villages in Nepal are disappearing due to out-migration. While some people have left to chase their dreams, the others are driven away by compulsion. Villages near the Baitadi headquarters however, have been chased away by monkeys.

==== Why Herne Katha? ====
People behind Herne Katha spent 15 years of their lives doing journalism. One day they realised the need to tell more beautiful and inspiring stories of people, the real people. 

üëÄüëÄüëÄ Herne Katha üëÄüëÄüëÄ
Herne Katha is a web series produced by Tana Bana Digital in Nepal. We tell stories of people in the format of short documentaries. New episode of Herne Katha is published on  every  alternate Tuesdays (15 days) on YouTube. You can also watch Herne  Katha on Kantipur  Television every Tuesday 6:30 PM.

üíåüíåüíå Share your Story üíåüíåüíå

üé®üé®üé® For all Creatives üé®üé®üé®
Have an idea about anything? Anything related to telling people's stories in bold and beautiful style. Share your ideas with us. We love ideas.

snippet.title: Salaar Teaser | Prabhas, Prashanth Neel, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Hombale Films, Vijay Kiragandur
snippet.description:
THE MOST VIOLENT MEN... CALLED ONE MAN... THE MOST VIOLENT üî•
Presenting our next feature #SalaarCeaseFire to the world

From the Makers of  "KGF: Chapter 1 & 2," &  the visionary director Prashanth Neel, comes a film that will push the boundaries of cinematic brilliance, presenting you the official teaser of "Salaar", featuring the powerhouse talents of Prabhas, Prithviraj, Shruthi Haasan, Tinu Anand, Eshwari Rao, Jagapathi Babu, Sriya Reddy, Garuda Ram.  
Brace yourself for an extraordinary tale of rebellion filled with power-packed action and impactful music by Ravi Basrur. 
Rebel Star Prabhas shines as Salaar, Directed by Prasanth Neel, and produced by Hombale Films, this teaser offers a thrilling glimpse into the intense narrative and mind-blowing visuals that await you. 
Get Ready to Rebel with us and witness the most violent man on screens this Sep 28th,2023.
